OL,3,CYouth club officially opens new
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,FA youth club has officially opened its
OL,7,Fnew refurbished premises after
OL,8,Freceiving a #1.3 million Youth
OL,9,FInvestment Fund grant.
OL,11,FHAFWAY, which as been rooted in Bolton
OL,12,Fsince 1998, has been helping young
OL,13,Fpeople in the area access sport, life
OL,14,Fskills, mentoring and Duke of
OL,15,FEdinburgh's Award activities for 28
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
