OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782134325
OL,3,CYouth club officially opens new
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,FAround 100 people, made up of past
OL,7,Fattendees, local families, volunteers
OL,8,Fand trustees attended the opening on
OL,9,FHalliwell Road, where there was a red
OL,10,Fribbon cut by Mayor of Bolton -
OL,11,FCouncillor Mohammed Iqbal to
OL,12,Fofficially signify the opening of the
OL,13,Fnew hub.
OL,15,FThe afternoon was hosted by two of
OL,16,FHAFWAY's attendees Zac Fraser and Zayn
OL,17,FTeemil who teed up video packages and
OL,18,Falso introduced the afternoon's
OL,19,Fspeakers to the stage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
