PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782134325
OL,3,CYouth club officially opens new
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,FFormer HAFWAY attendee Adam Nawaz took
OL,7,Fthe stage to talk about how the
OL,8,Fencouragement and support of HAFWAY
OL,9,Fstaff helped him build friendships and
OL,10,Fself-belief ultimately leading him to
OL,11,Fstudying law at university.
OL,13,FThis was followed up by speeches from
OL,14,Fthe HAFWAY chair Susan Pilling, the
OL,15,FMayor of Bolton and project manager
OL,16,FMoira Frew.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
