OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782134325
OL,3,CYouth club officially opens new
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,FAfter the short speeches, guests were
OL,7,Fthen invited to have a look around the
OL,8,Ffacility, sampling the video games,
OL,9,Fpool table and podcast recording
OL,10,Fstudio.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the event, Moira Frew,
OL,13,FProject Manager at HAFWAY, said: "This
OL,14,FHub is about so much more than bricks
OL,15,Fand mortar. It is about belonging,
OL,16,Fsafety, relationships and opportunity.
OL,26,@uD@bOU
