CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1782134325
OL,3,CYouth club officially opens new
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,F"It is about young people having a
OL,7,Fplace where they are known, valued and
OL,8,Fsupported to grow. When young people
OL,9,Fare given the right support,
OL,10,Fencouragement and opportunities, they
OL,11,Fcan go on to achieve things they may
OL,12,Fnever have thought possible."
OL,14,FBetween January and May 2026 alone,
OL,15,FHAFWAY supported 524 young people and
OL,16,Frecorded 5,112 attendees, highlighting
OL,17,Fthe need for free, accessible youth
OL,18,Fprovision in the area.
